E,Cash,Systems,provides,South,Africa,with,a,secure,online,payment,platform,for,online,merchants,The,E,Cash,API,is,offered,in,two,formats,Direct,API,through,a,securely,hosted,WSDL,enabling,direct,integration,via,a,web,service,and,redirect,API,integration,that,interacts,with,the,E,Cash,gateway,via,HTTPS,The,API,is,available,after,contract,setup,and,an,application,has,been,submitted,and,approved